com.appboy.configuration

Class AppboyConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.appboy.configuration.AppboyConfig

  • public class AppboyConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    Configuration for the Braze SDK. This configuration has full parity with use of xml configuration. Any key found in the `appboy.xml` configuration is configurable here. For all parameters of the built AppboyConfig object, any field will be set to null if not set in the builder.

      • getIsSessionStartBasedTimeoutEnabled

        public java.lang.Boolean getIsSessionStartBasedTimeoutEnabled()
        Gets whether the session timeout behavior is session-start or session-end based. When true, the session timeout and eventual session end is calculated using the timestamp of the start of the session. When false, the session timeout and eventual session end is calculated using the end of the session.
        See Also:
        getIsSessionStartBasedTimeoutEnabled()
